title: CDDIS_SLR_products_poseop
summary: Station position and Earth Orientation Parameters (EOPs) solutions derived from analysis of Satellite Laser Ranging (SLR) data. These products are the generated by analysis centers in support of the International Laser Ranging Service (ILRS) and combined by the ILRS analysis coordinator to form the official ILRS EOP and station position product (daily and weekly).
